title: Farm Income for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1968. Data Are Billions Of Dollars At Annual Rates. Source: Data Through 1962 Are From Survey Of Current Business, August 1965; Data For 1963-1968 Are From July Issues Of Survey Of Current Business.

This NBER data series q08276b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
